  "text": [
      { 
        "id": "215555119f73436fcf655bdb298b3235", 
        "cn": "盼望着，盼望着，东风来了，春天的脚步近了。", 
        "pinyin": "pan4|wang4|zhe1|pan4|wang4|zhe1|dong1|feng1|lai2|le5|chun1|tian1|de5|jiao3|bu4|jin4|le5",
        "src":"assets/demo/audios/MOE_CZYW_7A_U01_L02_CYLD_kongling.mp3", 
        "align":"left", 
        "duration":"1698" 
      },
      {
        "id": "215555119f73436fcf655bdb298b3236", 
        "cn": "一切都像刚睡醒的样子，欣欣然张开了眼。山朗润起来了，水涨起来了，太阳的脸红起来了。 ", 
        "pinyin": "yi1|qie4|dou1|xiang4|gang1|shui4|xing3|de5|yang4|zi3|xin1|xin1|ran2|zhang1|kai3|le5|yan3|shan1|lang3|run4|qi3|lai2|le5|shui3|zhang3|qi3|lai2|le5|tai4|yang2|de5|lian3|hong2|qi3|lai2|le5",
        "src":"assets/demo/audios/MOE_CZYW_7A_U01_L02_CYLD_kongling.mp3", 
        "align":"left", 
        "duration":"1698" 
      },
      {
        "id": "215555119f73436fcf655bdb298b3237", 
        "cn": "小草偷偷地从土里钻出来，嫩嫩的，绿绿的。园子里，田野里，瞧去，一大片一大片满是的。", 
        "pinyin": "xiao3|cao3|tou1|tou1|de5|cong2|tu3|li3|zuan1|chu1|lai2|nen4|nen4|de5|lv4|lv4|de5|yuan2|zi3|li3|tian2|ye3|li3|qiao2|qu4|yi1|da4|pian4|yi1|da4|pian4|man3|shi4|de5",
        "src":"assets/demo/audios/MOE_CZYW_7A_U01_L02_CYLD_kongling.mp3", 
        "align":"left", 
        "duration":"1698" 
      },
      {
        "id": "215555119f73436fcf655bdb298b3238", 
        "cn": "坐着，躺着，打两个滚，踢几脚球，赛几趟跑，捉几回迷藏。", 
        "pinyin": "zuo4|zhe5|tang3|zhe5|da3|liang3|ge4|gun3|ti1|ji3|jiao3|qiu2|sai4|ji3|tang4|pao3|zhuo1|ji3|hui2|mi1|cang2",
        "src":"assets/demo/audios/MOE_CZYW_7A_U01_L02_CYLD_kongling.mp3", 
        "align":"left", 
        "duration":"1698" 
      },
      { 
        "id": "215555119f73436fcf655bdb298b3239", 
        "cn": "盼望着，盼望着，东风来了，春天的脚步近了。", 
        "pinyin": "pan4|wang4|zhe1|pan4|wang4|zhe1|dong1|feng1|lai2|le5|chun1|tian1|de5|jiao3|bu4|jin4|le5",
